title: Jisua lenghordwngswi
lyrics:
Jisua lenghordwngswi, gaowijwng lwgwse -2
Jiuni derayao -2
(A)
Lubwinai dongwmwng, gwbangthar songsarao
Mabwrwi ang derhasart janw
Dukhuni dwikhongao, ang gabrobl
Swr dongw angkhou bwkhangnw -2
Oh . . Porbu, Nwngnw jiu, nwngnw lama arw swithwa-2
(B)
Mwdwi nonga be, onnaini nerswnsw
Zion harikhou sushrang hagra
Thwi nonga be papni suthur sw
Khwmsi songsarao bekheosart janai -2
Benw  hagou nwng papni suthurjwng daoha hwnw -2
